-Phase milestones:
-  Phase 6: set_baseline() will replace the fixed _clean_kcs_baseline with a
-            learned 90th–95th percentile of locally measured clean-sky Kcs.
-  Phase 8: set_gamma() will be wired to operator config in api.conf.
